e51a11b5-652c-4dd6-aeee-549c55072446?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/e51a11b5-652c-4dd6-aeee-549c55072446" class="r-13x3mc7" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="6d43f1df-1d82-4c44-b6cc-4f28bd69e528" class="r-bvuzk0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Supporting healthy neurotransmitters (so mood feels brighter)</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="88e4263d-0bd2-4510-9bda-395cfa5f5d30" data-list="Dot" class="r-dpjoxq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>This isn’t a stimulant.</p><p>It doesn’t make you jittery or spike your heart rate.</p><p><br></p><p>It helps your cells work the way they’re supposed to so you work the way you’re supposed to.</p></span></div><button data-rid="72717328-156f-4b83-b58a-485450f23ad5" tabindex="0" role="link" class="text r-rpm26x alchemy-rte"><div data-rid="0d17ce5b-cc38-4436-afe7-fd2e997299a3" class="r-1ojf41e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Shop Just Blue™</p></span></div></button></div></div></div><div data-rid="08808a5a-1e7f-4bbf-a285-fc4f7c3c0f8a" class="r-1mli2j7"><div class="r-ym08j7" data-rid="1"><div data-rid="bf08931f-c671-46bc-98ed-b3e1a5978da4" class="r-7x6hwp"><div data-rid="99a0a3e3-fbfa-479c-aaf7-37e235dbf031" class="r-zu4zxw"><div data-rid="8a4068a3-fdf4-468e-a147-371e44d0f23b" class="r-hktvk1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h2>How Methylene Blue Restores Energy In the Cell</h2></span></div><div data-rid="3d69a017-17dc-4e11-a025-5e99dc4f0407" data-bold="" class="r-f2hnm1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Mitochondria produce ATP by moving electrons through the electron transport chain. But stress, aging, and inflammation can block parts of this pathway, especially at Complex II and III.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Methylene blue is unique in that it can bypass bottlenecks in the chain.</strong></p><p><br></p><p>When the chain is blocked, Methylene Blue acts as an electron cycler, delivering electrons straight to Cytochrome C and Complex IV. This restores ATP production.</p></span></div><div data-rid="c80bc47d-ab6a-494b-9dfe-557c9b36ebbd" data-list="Dot" class="r-1apuysj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>This helps:</p><ul><li><p>maintain ATP production under stress</p></li><li><p>reduce excess oxidative byproducts</p></li><li><p>keep cellular energy flowing more efficiently</p></li></ul></span></div></div><div data-rid="a53773f8-5a9b-4e5d-8a46-0877f0311081" class="r-1e0o3ut"><picture data-rid="29ca9e1d-cf2f-449b-bef6-760d85591740" class="r-1jg25ow"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/0fce8d37-5929-4b9d-a01d-a1dba00414c8?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/d131ac63-5ca5-400f-ac76-24c103bc6687?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/d131ac63-5ca5-400f-ac76-24c103bc6687?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/d131ac63-5ca5-400f-ac76-24c103bc6687" alt="Illustration of a mitochondrion with labeled sections: inner membrane, outer membrane, matrix, intermembrane." class="r-1nofiza" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="354e3216-daf1-49de-be4c-f1e1809bb399" class="r-13hpaox"><picture data-rid="da7af040-991d-4898-bdca-5297c9689851" class="r-irdwso"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/4477b3f1-6767-4d55-9f78-2aaeae3afd90?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/4477b3f1-6767-4d55-9f78-2aaeae3afd90?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/4477b3f1-6767-4d55-9f78-2aaeae3afd90?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/4477b3f1-6767-4d55-9f78-2aaeae3afd90" class="r-19l2sac" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="1f0b3a12-ea1a-4be8-bf15-e55f378ed064" class="r-1ssdg3l"><div data-rid="1f721a88-1aea-4aeb-a135-698dfdf542e8" class="r-18bbbzk"><div data-rid="c9c8ac83-4832-42e1-83f4-d4d6deb52378" class="r-1m8j79b alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Methylene Blue Effect</p></span></div><div data-rid="7d9d0349-39e7-4d44-99cb-9d84a02143af" class="r-1t89g3z"><div data-rid="8ff023de-a7c8-4e1f-a79d-fb35d582b180" class="r-1oyzusq"><div data-rid="8f21eded-0d52-4f92-9771-1ddec3a51fa2" class="r-onif3u alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Before Methylene Blue</p></span></div><div data-rid="bad486a5-d175-484d-92da-0c127795ed68" class="r-kzltsn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>After Methylene Blue</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="d8029fc7-7a15-4159-9b80-a447385828e9" class="r-1q7hxu1"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/c1c051f8-754a-48ec-83ae-e56395c583f4?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/c1c051f8-754a-48ec-83ae-e56395c583f4?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/c1c051f8-754a-48ec-83ae-e56395c583f4?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/c1c051f8-754a-48ec-83ae-e56395c583f4" alt="Color-enhanced brain scans showing purple and green sections on a black background." class="r-1jmnv5l" loading="lazy"/></picture><div data-rid="98805508-7aca-4da0-b095-b6bd1ad70aa2" class="r-1ys13y5"></div></div><div data-rid="b73760e9-d9a1-4ea0-9c03-f28f1b0d2530" class="r-1ty2q9v alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>This is a representation of how Methylene Blue works, not a real brain scan. It is for educational and demonstrative purposes only.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="e3aca600-0148-4434-a4d8-f83cb6e48657" class="r-ytvk2b"><div data-rid="3b66b216-134b-4f76-9d2b-81f7c93c4186" class="r-1e9wzoq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>As you age, your cells don’t power you the way they used to. When mitochondria slow down and ATP drops, your clarity, focus, and energy fade right along with it. That tired-for-no-reason feeling often starts with cells that can’t make enough fuel.</p><p><br></p><p>Methylene Blue helps at the source. Trusted in medicine for over a century, it supports the part of your mitochondria that needs it most the electron transport chain, where your cells actually create ATP.</p><p><br></p><p>And when your cells can produce energy efficiently again, everything shifts. Your mind feels clearer, your focus sharpens, and you finally feel more like yourself powered from the inside out.</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="deff8e37-2ef3-4030-ac83-fcf9f31f6abf" class="r-wio2kt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>This is a representation of how Methylene Blue works, not a real brain scan. It is for educational and demonstrative purposes only.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="cee45cd8-9f74-42fd-882e-6cc6e9b28e8f" class="r-1l7at1i"><div data-rid="7247b023-1653-4211-bb9c-cf3bbf49a532" class="r-1h2479k"><div data-rid="6457d5c1-9b02-4a06-9df9-a6992b650d6d" class="r-b4jv97"><div data-rid="6724d823-2401-4032-8f6c-7f07f8c9d36d" class="r-x3lqwg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h2>Backed By Over 100 Years of Research</h2></span></div><div data-rid="cffb3fda-1c19-48b5-bf3f-da70439ac149" class="r-19foyz4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Methylene blue has been studied for over a century, and modern research continues to show impressive results.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="af35e570-49d7-4bdc-8c02-b1c388ca5660" class="r-kwq093"><div data-rid="23387d1a-2b3b-4bb3-9928-3dd062ddb528" class="r-1h0bj3u"><div data-rid="bf5ab450-6dce-4d7c-923b-537bb0d4137a" class="r-2dzdfs"><div data-rid="3397c496-874f-4a4c-a9e4-e8963a756f09" class="r-1u6w8qh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>+22</p></span></div><div data-rid="f6a0364c-8e48-435f-8728-f1d0152a7538" class="r-1qqwcqc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>%</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="bec33a65-f000-4d3d-975b-491134e5ac3b" class="r-b4miku alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>more energy flowing to the parts of your brain that drive focus and clarity*</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="4f3e8ccb-4f54-4885-8b65-0746a474a47a" class="r-1ok868b"><div data-rid="3a38fa62-1885-4148-99cf-cfa958fb1cf7" class="r-uqjqmh"><div data-rid="55e5d318-f6e2-40f7-b0a5-a32f1340630f" class="r-1w9bx4l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>~35</p></span></div><div data-rid="7623b926-1149-43b1-a97e-4aeaae76ff88" class="r-1h9av9h alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>%</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="68f35b8e-06d5-47e5-bfcb-1d848994245b" class="r-ulunjc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>more cellular energy in humans exposed to methylene blue*</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="6a44c56e-690e-44ad-9e26-ac0355e04ee0" class="r-s3x2xl"><div data-rid="ab19a2ab-d5f8-41cd-a4b2-dc61fa34d3f4" class="r-q1ngh4"><div data-rid="d2bb5bfe-7f9b-4ee7-83e6-5273de2988c8" class="r-1l46o43 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>~30</p></span></div><div data-rid="30299e0c-434e-448d-81d9-6da65335e10c" class="r-j4e52e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>%</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="9682f39b-3f6d-426b-98b9-66efca8edabc" class="r-a0l77z alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>improvement in the brain’s oxygen-to-energy process*</p></span></div></div></div><button data-rid="ee24cf3a-b3bc-40df-9908-4cf2dbe41320" tabindex="0" role="link" class="text r-1jpunis alchemy-rte"><div data-rid="8cf67942-c719-482a-a246-f00a50664ef4" class="r-113u06o alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Shop Just Blue™</p></span></div></button></div><div data-rid="ccee190e-ae9d-4b3f-9f55-bac4df00d8c0" data-bg="blur" class="r-h013ej"><div data-rid="bd15dc70-d1da-469d-b2a0-02e412296fce" class="r-riwfb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>*These results come from early research, cell and animal models, and small human studies. They do not guarantee specific outcomes and are provided for educational purposes only.</p></span></div><div data-rid="48e78ce6-ab59-4034-b320-fec293e5e141" class="r-1i191dg"><div data-rid="5c42d257-025f-45b7-8070-733074c471b6" class="r-63sf2u alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0046585&">Source A</a></p></span></div><div data-rid="8c3464d1-20fd-4b8d-a179-1075228cfdac" class="r-1knnaj6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://www.mdpi.com/2673-5261/6/3/16">Source B</a></p></span></div><div data-rid="29e561fd-9c3e-4923-84f3-66eee502bf64" class="r-1vhpqtv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14724055/">Source C</a></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="5115ae71-af6c-4cbd-95f2-5fc8430774e1" class="r-s8ant5"><div class="r-wli2to" data-rid="1"><div data-rid="eddc92ef-dbf2-4751-9a9d-3d470609b535" class="r-lg62fi"><div data-rid="de7434bf-4551-4e08-97c0-934291382d06" class="r-mto9k4"><div data-rid="8b87a579-eef0-4231-96c2-f37b2819f91b" class="r-nj5d4e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h2>Refuel Your Cells And See How You Feel</h2></span></div><div data-rid="30030aed-0299-4e0d-b965-e146e8cd74d9" class="r-74ulug alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Low-dose methylene blue delivers cle